---
import Layout from "../../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import app from "../../../images/bg/joinnow.webp";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
---

<Layout title="التسجيل | المناديب" lang="ar">
  <section
    class="hero relative bg-drivers_registration_mobile_ar xs:bg-drivers_registration_md_ar 3xl:bg-drivers_registration_lg_ar bg-cover bg-center bg-no-repeat flex items-center after:bg-black/70 after:xs:bg-transparent after:xs:bg-gradient-to-r from-black/40 from-0% to-black/70 to-80% after:size-full after:absolute after:z-0"
  >
    <div class="container section-container z-10">
      <div
        class="fade flex flex-col gap-7 text-white text-right lg:w-[45%]"
        data-animation="animate-fade animate-duration-[1500ms]"
      >
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl">قد مع لأجلك.</h1>
        <h4 class="text-base md:text-xl">
          انضم إلينا في لأجلك كسائق وكن جزءًا من فريق ديناميكي مكرس لتقديم خدمات
          توصيل فعّالة.
        </h4>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="bg-white">
    <div
      class="fade container section-container flex items-center flex-col justify-between lg:flex-row gap-y-10"
      data-animation="animate-fade animate-duration-[1000ms]"
    >
      <div
        class="lg:max-w-[432px] max-h-[745px] overflow-hidden order-2 lg:order-1"
      >
        <Image
          src={app}
          alt="app"
          class="w-full h-full pointer-events-none"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>
      <div
        class="flex flex-col justify-center gap-y-10 lg:w-1/2 order-1 lg:order-2"
      >
        <div class="text-right space-y-2">
          <h2 class="">كيفية البدء</h2>
          <p>اربح المزيد أثناء التنقل مع لأجلك - قد، سلّم، وزد دخلك!</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <ol class="[counter-reset:my-sec-counter] space-y-8">
            <li
              class="relative flex flex-row gap-4 [counter-increment:my-sec-counter] before:content-[counter(my-sec-counter)] before:flex before:size-6 before:flex-shrink-0 before:bg-primaryOrange before:rounded-full before:text-white before:justify-center before:items-center before:font-medium before:text-sm"
            >
              <div class="flex flex-col space-y-2">
                <h4 class="leading-none">تحميل</h4>
                <p>
                  قم بتحميل تطبيق لأجلك من <a
                    href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.leajlak.captainapp&hl=en_US"
                    target="”_blank”"
                    class="underline underline-offset-2">متجر جوجل</a
                  > أو <a
                    href="https://apps.apple.com/tr/app/leajlak/id6444185447"
                    target="”_blank”"
                    class="underline underline-offset-2">متجر آبل</a
                  >.
                </p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li
              class="relative flex flex-row gap-4 [counter-increment:my-sec-counter] before:content-[counter(my-sec-counter)] before:flex-shrink-0 before:flex before:size-6 before:bg-primaryOrange before:rounded-full before:text-white before:justify-center before:items-center before:font-medium before:text-sm"
            >
              <div class="flex flex-col space-y-2">
                <h4 class="leading-none">تسجيل</h4>
                <p>قم بتعبئة التفاصيل اللازمة وتقديم المستندات المطلوبة.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li
              class="relative flex flex-row gap-4 [counter-increment:my-sec-counter] before:content-[counter(my-sec-counter)] before:flex-shrink-0 before:flex before:size-6 before:bg-primaryOrange before:rounded-full before:text-white before:justify-center before:items-center before:font-medium before:text-sm"
            >
              <div class="flex flex-col space-y-2">
                <h4 class="leading-none">تعلم</h4>
                <p>تعرف على عملياتنا وابدأ بسرعة.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li
              class="relative flex flex-row gap-4 [counter-increment:my-sec-counter] before:content-[counter(my-sec-counter)] before:flex-shrink-0 before:flex before:size-6 before:bg-primaryOrange before:rounded-full before:text-white before:justify-center before:items-center before:font-medium before:text-sm"
            >
              <div class="flex flex-col space-y-2">
                <h4 class="leading-none">ابدأ</h4>
                <p>ابدأ في قبول مهام التوصيل وابدأ في كسب دخل إضافي.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ol>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
